"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.12.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.12.1</span> 标题：锤子（hammer）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：הַלְמוּת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：halmuth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:26\">JDG 5:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מַקֶּבֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：maqavah, maqeveth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:21\">JDG 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:7\">1KI 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:12\">ISA 44:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:4\">JER 10:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִקְשָׁה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：miqshah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:18\">EXO 25:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:31\">EXO 25:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:36\">EXO 25:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:7\">EXO 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:17\">EXO 37:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:22\">EXO 37:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:4\">NUM 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:4\">NUM 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:2\">NUM 10:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：פַּטִּישׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：patish)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:7\">ISA 41:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:29\">JER 23:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:23\">JER 50:23</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：רִקֻּעַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：riqua‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:3\">NUM 17:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἐλατός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：elatos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir50:16\">SIR 50:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ὁλοσφύρητος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：olosfurētos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir50:9\">SIR 50:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σφῦρα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：sfura)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:28\">SIR 38:28</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0370_hammer.jpg\" alt=\"木锤\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">木锤 (© Giovanni Dall&#x27;Orto, Attribution, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>锤子是一种工具，长约30厘米（1英尺），有一个通常用木头做成的手柄，手柄上固定着一个石头、木头或金属（不太常见）的头。手柄装在锤头的孔内。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/BOT-0022_worker_hammer_hans.jpg\" alt=\"用锤子工作的人\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">用锤子工作的人 (Elbert Boot © United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>锤子有多种用途，例如砸碎或修整建筑石块、将钉子或橛子敲到木头里面，或将橛子敲入地里。铁匠也用锤子来使热铁成型。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯来文<em>miqshah</em> 的意思不太确定。这个词似乎是指工匠处理金属物件的成果，即“锤打出来的作品”或“打好的工件”。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
